import VersoBlog

open Verso.Genre.Blog

#doc (Page) "Lean AI formalization leaderboard" =>

This site tracks public results for the `lean-eval` benchmark: hard Lean
formalization problems intended to measure mathematical formalization ability
rather than original mathematical discovery.

The homepage leaderboard is generated from public result records and benchmark
metadata. Expand a row to inspect a model's most notable solved problems and,
when available, follow links to public proofs.
